<script>
import { Line, mixins } from "vue-chartjs";
const { reactiveProp } = mixins;
export default {
  extends: Line,
  mixins: [reactiveProp],
  props: {
    options: {},
    propData: {
      type: Array,
      default: null
    }
  },
  data () {
    return {
      options: {},
    }
  },
  mounted() {
    this.renderChart(this.chartdata, this.options);
  },
};
</script>
